I am notifying today the Exchange and Gift Division of the Library that my box of manuscripts is on its way by Railway Express.





Sincerely yours,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: VICTOR REYNOLDS

CC, 1 p.

Ithaca, N.Y.





January 8, 1958 [1959]

